### Calculator REST API Demo - Test Requests

# Health Check
GET http://localhost:5127/api/calculator/health

###

# Addition using GET endpoint
GET http://localhost:5127/api/calculator/add?a=15&b=25

###

# Subtraction using GET endpoint  
GET http://localhost:5127/api/calculator/subtract?a=50&b=20

###

# Multiplication using GET endpoint
GET http://localhost:5127/api/calculator/multiply?a=8&b=7

###

# Division using GET endpoint
GET http://localhost:5127/api/calculator/divide?a=100&b=4

###

# Division by zero test (should return error)
GET http://localhost:5127/api/calculator/divide?a=10&b=0

###

# Addition using POST endpoint with JSON
POST http://localhost:5127/api/calculator/calculate
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstNumber": 123.45,
    "secondNumber": 67.89,
    "operation": "Add"
}

###

